<paragraph blockId="18.[112,649,524,654]" pageId="18" pageNumber="343">
MORPHOLOGY. — TL from 
<quantity box="[405,573,524,548]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.5" metricValueMax="8.6" metricValueMin="2.4" pageId="18" pageNumber="343" unit="mm" value="550.0" valueMax="860.0" valueMin="240.0">240 to 860 mm</quantity>
; 23-25 MSR, smooth; 198-216 Ven, smooth, 43-62 Sc, paired; anal single; loreal longer than high; 8 supralabials; 8-10 infralabials; 2, sometimes 1 preoculars; 2 postoculars; temporal scale formula 1 + 2 + 3.
</paragraph>
