<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="343" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="18.[112,648,679,862]" pageId="18" pageNumber="343">
DISTRIBUTION. — This species is mainly a forest-dweller. The northern limit of its range is in the region of Aledjo where new specimens were recently collected. It might also be present in the region of 
<collectingRegion box="[439,489,759,783]" country="Togo" name="Kara" pageId="18" pageNumber="343">Kara</collectingRegion>
. Previously this species had been recorded from 
<collectingCountry box="[407,455,785,809]" name="Togo" pageId="18" pageNumber="343">Togo</collectingCountry>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="MATSCHIE P." box="[487,644,785,809]" pageId="18" pageNumber="343" pagination="207 - 215" refId="ref28100" refString="MATSCHIE P. 1893. - Die Reptilien und Amphibien Togogebietes. Mittheilungen von Forschungsreisenden und Gelehrten aus den deutschen Schutzgebieten, mit Benutzung amtlicher Quellen 6: 207 - 215." type="journal article" year="1893">Matschie (1893)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="STERNFELD L." box="[112,280,812,836]" pageId="18" pageNumber="343" pagination="207 - 236" refId="ref29004" refString="STERNFELD L. 1908 b. - Die Schlangenfauna Togos. Mittheilungen Zoologischen Museum in Berlin 4: 207 - 236." type="journal article" year="1908">Sternfeld (1908b</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="STERNFELD L." box="[292,383,812,836]" pageId="18" pageNumber="343" refId="ref29026" refString="STERNFELD L. 1909. - Die Schlangen Togos, in Die Fauna der deutschen Kolonien 1 (1): iv + 29 p., map." type="book" year="1909">1909: 12</bibRefCitation>
), 
<bibRefCitation author="HULSELMANS J. L. J. &amp; VERHEYEN W. N." pageId="18" pageNumber="343" pagination="200 - 204" refId="ref27452" refString="HULSELMANS J. L. J. &amp; VERHEYEN W. N. 1970. - Contribution a l'herpetologie de la Republique du Togo: Liste preliminaire des serpents recoltes par la deuxieme mission zoologique belge au Togo. Revue de Zoologie et de Botanique africaines 82 (1 - 2): 200 - 204." type="journal article" year="1970">Hulselmans &amp; Verheyen (1970)</bibRefCitation>
, and 
<bibRefCitation author="HULSELMANS J. L. J. &amp; DE VREE F. &amp; VAN DER STRAETEN E." box="[236,480,838,862]" pageId="18" pageNumber="343" pagination="46 - 49" refId="ref27570" refString="HULSELMANS J. L. J., DE VREE F. &amp; VAN DER STRAETEN E. 1971. - Contribution a l'herpetologie de la Republique du Togo: liste preliminaire des serpents recoltes par la troisieme mission zoologique belge au Togo. Revue de Zoologie et de Botanique africaines 84 (1 - 2): 46 - 49." type="journal article" year="1971">
